{"tid":1369164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「聽日打算去元朗國走私老婆餅嘅入黎」","createTime":"2019-07-26T15:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T01:39:17.000Z","uid":74828,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"84f63d001973d36e4a63bc3b1d8cd13eee2177a2","tid":1369164,"uid":74828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:39:56.000Z","msg":"由於元朗行人路出名窄但多自由行、難得元朗終於獨立成國！點可以唔搶先成為第一批元朗國自由行旅客？<br />\n<br />\n1. 去元朗國自由行<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記得帶喼，隨地喼放戰利品</span></span></strong>，例如走私老婆餅。<br />\n<br />\n2. 自由行最緊要小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">千其唔好行出馬路，寧願慢慢行</span></span></strong>，反正元朗行人路爆滿都係週末必見奇景。<br />\n<br />\n3. 有鑒於元朗國剛受到恐怖襲擊，請各遊客<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">帶備旅遊裝備保護一眾熱愛購物嘅香港人</span></span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n大家一於好好享受元朗國的美食、購物旅遊，有時間就捉下稀有精靈。 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記得聽日所有行動世界會睇住，如果聽日我地主動衝嘅話文宣巴絲點都幫你唔到。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"b2e235f98d8579ff7216b11ba777aaf248facbe8","tid":1369164,"uid":263659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:40:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拉出元朗馬路 名義公民拘捕</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1368670\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1368670</a>"},{"pid":"e2328b07d3360a6990e2bc7105377e5bd1dd8a69","tid":1369164,"uid":216789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:41:43.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"717d520b00898d5b2ace67ba859bff75dfc56e9b","tid":1369164,"uid":5172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223f2d2dc6f357f1a60d792cb279964dab22f8f0","tid":1369164,"uid":275975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:43:12.000Z","msg":"聽朝狗狗學堂畢業禮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5bda006a73953022928eed57f188d8314abebe","tid":1369164,"uid":74828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:51:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b53b6878d2fd825880162e44908af679d794951d","tid":1369164,"uid":74828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:55:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9eea21462d03115e2ce6e04ef5db216640eae7d3","tid":1369164,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:56:17.000Z","msg":"大家都眼目近日元朗新聞<br />\n咁都可以指麇為那 癲倒是非<br />\n<br />\n大家自問一下，<br />\n做下心理功課，諗下應對，<br />\n以免入村變入侵，又有人保家衛國。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 有人沖入，你跟唔跟<br />\n2. 村入面有人撩你，你沖唔沖<br />\n3. 有人打完手足，龜入村，你沖唔沖<br />\n4. 有人捉左手足入村，救唔救！<br />\n5. 警察三面圍迫，焗你入村<br />\n6. 圍村要交人，圍幾耐，點進行下一步<br />\n7. 如果非法遊行被捉，點做？<br />\n<br />\n一定要記者<br />\n拍片紀錄係最強大武器<br />\n<br />\n一定要先禮後兵<br />\n有聲公講清楚發生咩事，唔要得口號。<br />\n就算手捉被人捉左入村！"},{"pid":"138b6896ad0246c1e58dfe2b28e846f6858ce904","tid":1369164,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:56:20.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山, 做乜都好, 搵咗攻略睇先! <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再on 99 講有事退去寫字樓! </span></span><br />\n元朗有L寫字樓/商場你退!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nif 天水被人圍咗, 無交通工具, 跑online 離開元朗去洪水橋/屯門要行 1.5 至 2 小時! <br />\n即係<span style=\"color: blue;\">2倍老銅出支聯辦既距離</span>!<br />\n<br />\n做乜都好, 睇路呀!!! 唔好去送頭呀!!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/EzULh8v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEzULh8v.png&h=8cea8ccc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n地圖傳送門:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1361703/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1361703/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"5e006b6a5d97e808cea84e29494beddceeba6716","tid":1369164,"uid":74828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:58:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6f6f721d8bd58c539c39842554e2130912bb78a","tid":1369164,"uid":74828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:03:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2467ab3a41dcaca51927634d0e051fa10861e194","tid":1369164,"uid":276208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:03:40.000Z","msg":"借位一用<br />\n<br />\n請幫推到鄉民見到，希望聽日可以相安無事<br />\n[投訴懶人包] 反對套丁及冒充原居民 「修補撕裂，由我做起，幫助原居民保家衛族」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1369127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1369127</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: blue;\">齊上齊落，支持五大訴求<br />\n支持圍村去黑，還我平靜鄉郊<br />\n反恐反黑，由投訴撚做起</span></em>"},{"pid":"e2abab186e1e1ccf0cf9dc7ad4c982cdd2d87dd7","tid":1369164,"uid":74828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:11:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b62d89b222286df92de80c75c2b96f9811dc163","tid":1369164,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T01:39:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>各位手足<br />\n萬事小心<br />\n<br />\n#一個都不能少<br />\n#727</strong></span></span>"}]}